       Tankkor plows over the snow drift and comes down hard, and the bots on 
top of him go into the battle plan, taking a target and proceeding after it. 
Tankkor, as he was promised, got the first shots. He targets Endbringer, and 
releases a few shots from his powerful tank turrets while the other 
Predacons, Rampage included, unlease thier well stocked ammo.
